    "abstract": "<jats:label>1.</jats:label>\n                <jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>The pandemic of the COVID-19 disease extended from China across the north-temperate zone, and more recently to the tropics and southern hemisphere. We find no evidence that spread rates decline with temperatures above 20 \u00b0C, suggesting that the COVID-19 disease is unlikely to behave as a seasonal respiratory virus.</jats:p>",
